Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:05.00,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}As times{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10} chan{\r\be10}ge,\Ndifficult cases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:09.01,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's case is about a face pack!\NCan makeup hide the evidence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:10.81,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:13.18,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:15.55,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:44.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! It's Beika Security!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:48.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:58.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! We're opening the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:01:59.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do it!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:02.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:08.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Did I scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:09.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:12.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was putting my face pack on,\Nso I couldn't answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:16.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your security alarm went off...\Ndid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:18.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Must've been a glitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:22.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:27.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:31.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've crossed the infrared sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:34.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so sensitive that this happens once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:37.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, please be sure to lock up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:39.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, am I full!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:03:02.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,China has nothing on this place's Chinese cuisine! Don't you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:06.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Actually, ramen's pretty much the same anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's already this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:12.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s drama show is on tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! I'm coming home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:16.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:22.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:28.62,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,TM Securities Employee\NTakeo Izumi (25)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:28.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry! I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:32.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're driving, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:35.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it also your fault for crossing the street without paying attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:39.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your guys' deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:44.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Megure{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:47.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Police Investigation Section #1?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:50.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Mouri here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:54.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here? Oh, that doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What case are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:04:00.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! He's involved with a murder case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mouriâ€”!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:10.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:13.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:20.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just crossed paths with the peerless Kogoro Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:23.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I have no idea what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:28.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb! You can spout your excuses when we get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:31.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Would the police call a suspect on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:53.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought the suspect, as requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:59.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:05.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Takeo Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} were a suspect, we obviously wouldn't call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:09.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yeah, I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,TM Securities, Beika Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:18.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. You visited this home tonight, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:21.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, no... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:28.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You came at 8:00 exactly, and left at 8:40. Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the exact times...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:32.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know the times so exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:37.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on the security camera tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! So he did kill her, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:47.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left... Yes, at 8:50,\Nthe daughter stopped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:51.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim was still alive then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:55.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, security personnel saw her at 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:57.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Security personnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:06:02.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat snuck into the yard\Nand set off the security alarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:06.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I contacted Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to learn more about the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:13.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the victim, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:18.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikuko Kojima. She managed a chain of discount electronics stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:19.87,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Businesswoman\NIkuko Kojima (50)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:19.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was strangled to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:26.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that everyone is here, let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.93,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Victim's Daughter\NChihiro Kojima (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the victim's daughter, Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:34.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,First to Find Victim\NJuro Yoshioka (48)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:35.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one who found her, Yoshioka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:38.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:43.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The great detective, Kogoro Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:46.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kogoro Mouri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:50.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. According to the security video...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:55.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} arrived at 8:00, and left at 8:40.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:07:01.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} arrived at 8:50, and left at 9:10.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:05.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Yoshioka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} arrived at 9:20, discovered the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and called the police at 9:31.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume this is all correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:13.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's on tape, then of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:17.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Her own mother just died! Why is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:22.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it your mother was still alive when you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she was!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:27.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or what? Are you suggesting I killed my mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:30.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, nothing of the sort...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:37.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, that puts the time of death between 9:10 and 9:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the house locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:44.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The front door was apparently open\Nwhen Mr. Yoshioka arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:47.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All other doors were locked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:53.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning the killer was one of these three who used the front door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:59.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, time-wise, we can probably discount Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:02.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! He has a motive for killing my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:07.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was on the verge of being sued by her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:11.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasted 300 million of her money on a lousy investment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:20.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you pretended to leave\Nand snuck in when the coast was clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:24.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:28.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the time of death was between 9:10 and 9:20,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:31.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,time-wise, Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} couldn't have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:32.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:36.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember? It was around 9:40...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,9:40...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:40.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:41.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:47.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, he was with us in Beika at 9:40...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:54.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It'd take at least 50 to 60 minutes to get there by car...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's in the clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he could've done it somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The lady has a point!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:08.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Miss. Didn't you have a reason of your own to kill her, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:16.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mother severed all ties with her because of her fiancÃ©.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, her husband is behind bars...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:25.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if that were true,\Nwhy would I need to kill my mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:30.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you asked her for a loan,\Nbut were harshly brushed aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:35.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that that fueled a big family quarrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:41.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who argued with her\Nand said you'd kill her someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:49.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it would appear one of you two is the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:52.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what brought you here tonight, Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:55.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was called here. To be lectured at.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:59.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that made you snap and kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you get serious, you lousy detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lousy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:07.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what brought you here, Yoshioka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A work-related meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:16.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The circumstances definitely indicate it was one of these two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:30.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the tape. Let me know if you remember or notice anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:38.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} arrives at 8:00 on the dot and goes inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's at 8:40 exactly that he leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:50.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. The time is 8:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:55.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, 10 minutes later, Ms. Ikuko steps out to speak with the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:11:00.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So the victim was still alive at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:05.23,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What is it? Something seems different...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:09.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At 9:10, Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:17.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, at 9:20, Yoshioka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:21.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But as there's no response, he looks inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:24.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...and finds Ms. Ikuko dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rewind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:35.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why did you go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:40.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-To contact the police, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you go outside when there's a phone in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:51.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in shock. So I went to my car to get my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:54.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't blame him; he found a dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:57.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone who ran out shocked,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he did spend 10 minutes in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do for those 10 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:12.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And look, he's holding something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Care to explain, Yoshioka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:19.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:22.86,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}"Report â€” Ozawa Detective Agency"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:30.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So this shows that you embezzled money from the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:33.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be ruined if that were made public!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:36.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I came to talk with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:40.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that discussion ended with you killing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:44.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! She was already dead when I arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:46.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like we can really believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought if this document got out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:53.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be the prime suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:02.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So then you called the police after hiding it in your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:03.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:07.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can give us your excuses down at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:13.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it! She really was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:16.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta believe me! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:28.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What is it? Something isn't right about this body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:30.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She was dressed for bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.76,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}even though she was expecting visitors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's weird, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:42.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mouth is wide open, but there aren't any wrinkles at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:53.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's it! This was a true death mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:01.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Inspector. We're ready to take her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh no! lt'll be too late once the body is taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:09.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This body really is weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:14.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in a bathrobe, and with a face pack on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:16.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing unusual about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:17.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she was going to bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even though she was expecting company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely not how one looks before having company over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:25.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was her daughter coming over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:30.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yoshioka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was supposed to stop by after Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:33.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was strangled to death, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} pointed out that it's weird
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that her face pack has no wrinkles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:41.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:46.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It should have wrinkles if she was in pain with it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:15:01.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...the culprit applied the face pack after killing the victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:04.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And put her in the bathrobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:09.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was dressed like this when you were here, right, Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:14.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:15.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The security guards saw her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:22.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. When I came over due to a false alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was indeed dressed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:29.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, why would the killer redo her face pack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything seem strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:32.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:34.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it was her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:38.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her eyes, ears, or lips, for example?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:39.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her face was covered with the pack andâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:44.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised by how her bright purple lips
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,clashed with her white face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not wearing lipstick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:55.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean like Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s color?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:00.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That was the color!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:07.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! So you put the face pack on and met with the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:14.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being turned down for the loan caused you to kill your own mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:19.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first slip-up was the malfunctioning security alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was no response,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:24.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the guards would've entered the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:30.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised, you quickly decided to play the role of your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:33.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With a face pack and a robe, you could fool them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are mother and daughter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:42.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in your rush, you met them with your lipstick still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:46.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you had to remove your mother's lipstick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since packs are applied
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,after washing the face and removing makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:57.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I met the guards and put the face pack on my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:01.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was already dead when I got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows that she and I constantly fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:09.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought everyone would think I killed her, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:13.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to believe me! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:16.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's no question that she tried to cover things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:19.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But it doesn't serve as an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:23.02,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All it does is{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10} chan{\r\be10}ge the time of death to beâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If the time of death is{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10} chan{\r\be10}ged...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:33.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man Mouri says...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:44.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's strange. Why hasn't it turned up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:51.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, is it okay for me to leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:58.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll need to talk to you again at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oww!\N- Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:11.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! I told you not to hang around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:14.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:29.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:36.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:41.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we end this play if the main character leaves the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:44.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you mean, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:48.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally figured out who really killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:49.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:52.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you just said that Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:54.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said nothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:59.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I merely exposed her cover-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:03.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her unnecessary tampering altered the estimated time of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:08.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,which ironically created an alibi for the real killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:09.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The real killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:10.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Surely you're joking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:18.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You vouched that I was in Beika when the murder took place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:21.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if her testimony is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:26.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then the murder took place before 8:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:29.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you could have done it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:32.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! Are you saying you believe her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:37.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what proof do you have that I killed the woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:41.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Did your mother have poor eyesight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:48.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Y-Yes. But she always wore contacts instead of glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:51.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take another look at the victim's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:55.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe only her left contact is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the left one is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:02.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't any contacts in her belongings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use in looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:07.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the killer has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:14.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The missing contact lens is in your pants cuff, Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:19.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:24.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:28.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:31.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a place it could just happen to wind up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:35.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It could only happen to someone with direct contact with the victimâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:39.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the killer, in other words!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:50.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to sue me for all I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:54.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I only invested how she told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:59.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the minute we lost money, she blamed it all on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:04.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Anything but court!\NI'll pay it back, however long itâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:08.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked the land your parents live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:13.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could postpone things if they sold it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Butâ€”!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:17.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I already spoke with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:20.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've agreed to do anything to compensate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:24.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Family ties are such a wonderful thing, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:33.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She had to pay...\Nfor dragging my elderly parents into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:11.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work! You saved the day yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:12.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:17.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police lost a great man when you left the force!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:18.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.94,0:23:20.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:21.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:24.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Conan! Time to celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:25.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get some food on our way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:28.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More ramen, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:32.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! I'm not talking cheap food here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:33.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Alright!\N- Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:37.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll celebrate with pork ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:43.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured as much...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:47.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:53.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why is Oyama{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} sitting formally?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:57.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, one of you is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:02.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The blood on the table... And the tablecloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:06.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just as the dying message says,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.14,0:24:09.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}the killer is definitely that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.65,0:24:14.62,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.62,0:24:19.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Shogi
